# Project Overview

Gemini SDK 기반 AI 챗봇. pnpm 모노레포 (frontend + backend + shared).

## 폴더 구조

- `frontend/src/`: React 19 + Vite + Tailwind v4 (components/, pages/, hooks/, stores/, services/)
- `backend/src/`: NestJS v11 (modules/{auth,users,chat,gemini}/, common/, config/, database/)
- `shared/src/`: 공유 타입, 상수, 유틸리티

## DB 스키마

- **users**: id, email, password_hash, name, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at
- **conversations**: id, user_id, title, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at (User N:1)
- **messages**: id, conversation_id, role(user/assistant), content, created_at (Conversation N:1)
